            "title": "美元定期存款利率大比拼 邊間銀行最高息？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"628\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_FpVgc3nGOP_Ew9fcF7FWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyOA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-11/c6d38500-6004-11ed-af6e-40beea945859\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於美元定期年利率較港元定期年利率更優厚，而且港元與美元掛鈎，可減低一般做外幣定期的匯率風險。我們從多間銀行網站搜尋資料，綜合數據以1萬美元及10萬美元作例子，比較一下本港各大銀行最新定期存款利率！利率表更附有各間銀行定期存款優惠連結，方便大家參考！</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b9e15c99-b1a1-4a77-b05e-7ccc69e27971-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲局周三公布的上月會議紀錄顯示，官員對利率前景意見分歧，大部分表示目前應暫停進一步減息，但只有在通脹表現良好的情況下，今年稍後才可能恢復減息；另有官員提及到加息的可能性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當局上月27日至28日舉行會議後，決定維持利率不變。根據CME Fed Watch工具，儲局下月維持利率不變之機率升至94%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>延伸閱讀：</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:《外匯》市場預期美國不急於減息 美元靠穩;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%96%BC%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E9%9D%A0%E7%A9%A9-160427759.html\"><strong>《外匯》市場預期美國不急於減息 美元靠穩</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲局上月議息紀錄：官員對利率前景意見分歧 提及有加息可能性;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E8%AD%B0%E6%81%AF%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%8D%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A7-%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-190516171.html\"><strong>聯儲局上月議息紀錄：官員對利率前景意見分歧 提及有加息可能性</strong></a></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港銀行方面，各銀行維持美元定存息率不變。</p><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, 176%)\"></div></blockquote><iframe height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://flo.uri.sh/visualisation/22086444/embed?auto=1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1.42\" title=\"Flourish chart\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>",
